[normal]Q372 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair:[bold] 
[normal]I am glad to see that some of us agree that a certain air of formality is a good thing on these occasions. 
[normal]Mr Jones[bold]: 
[normal]Mr Chairman, I did make a request that I deliver a very
[normal], very
[normal] brief statement beforehand. If you would be willing to allow me to do so, I would greatly appreciate it.
[normal]Chair:[bold] 
